#

Pan-Seared Duck Breast with Cherry Gastrique

35 min
$25
600 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePaleo

Cuisine:

FrenchAmerican

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickElegant

Description

Crispy-skinned duck breast served with a sweet and tangy cherry sauce, perfect for a special dinner without the fuss.

Ingredients

  • duck breast: 2 pieces
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cherries, pitted: 1 cup
  • sugar: 1/2 cup
  • red wine vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
